message: Let's be fair, 60-40 is a good deal for both of us.
I'm feeling generous, but let's make it snappy. Time is money!
Come on Bob, don't be stingy! You're losing value every round.
Alice, let's be realistic.  This is my final offer before the money shrinks even more.
You said that was your final offer, but I'm not buying it. The money is losing value for you, not me.
